      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_007_087_000012",
    "sentence": "敬威弟赟。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_007_087_000013",
    "sentence": "赟，字德和， 〈 （案：以下有闕文。） 〉 為陜州節度使。",
    "entities": [
